divs: Sighting DetailsMy parents and I were over at the Superstition mountain Museum and we were taking pictures to remember our time there. Neither myself or parents saw anything in the sky during the times of the photographs. it wasnt until I uploaded the pictures onto the computer and went through them that i noticed that there was something in them . In my opinion the objects in the photo do not appear to be any type of aircraft that I know of ( airplane, helicopter). I am not surprised to see anything like this on camera but I just want an explanation.
